These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different games are played: go, scrabble, billiard, snooker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, horse, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, ship, train, tram
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person playing go is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
 6. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 7. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
 8. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 9. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
10. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person playing go##7
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
13. the person driving the tram is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Game   | snooker    | scrabble | billiard    | go   |
| Beverage   | fanta | soy-milk | sprite | hot-chocolate |
| Pet           | dog       | horse   | rabbit  | cat     |
| Transport     | bike      | train   | tram    | ship    |

