.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, boat, skateboard, snowmobile
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, thriller, time-travel
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, designer, writer, paramedic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 2. the writer is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
 3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the mechanic##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the writer##3
 6. the designer is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the mechanic##7
 8. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
10. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
11. the designer is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Transport          | subway   | skateboard       | snowmobile    | boat      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | time-travel | crime         | thriller   |
| Job   | paramedic   | mechanic  | designer       | writer |
| Sport         | golf      | volleyball  | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

