.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, designer, project-manager, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, martial-arts, zombie
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, apricot, blue, white
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, vegafina, blend, prince
 1. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 2. the prince-smoker is somewhere between the bartender and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
 3. the designer is the person who likes apricot##1
 4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
 5. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 6. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 7. the project-manager is not the person watching crime movies##6
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the social-worker##6
 9. the bartender is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
10. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the designer is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
12. the person who likes blue is the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Job           | social-worker | bartender | designer | project-manager |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | zombie    | crime    | martial-arts    |
| Color   | turquise        | white   | apricot   | blue         |
| Cigar           | vegafina          | dunhill       | prince   | blend           |

