.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, february, march
There 4 different types of food: banana, broccoli, cabbage, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, collecting, hiking, baking
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, ship, trike
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is the person eating cabbage##1
 3. the person eating banana is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
 4. the person eating cabbage is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
 5. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
 7. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the trike##7
10. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
11. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in february and the person eating spinach##7
13. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Birthday      | june | july      | march      | february |
| Food          | cabbage     | spinach   | banana   | broccoli |
| Hobby   | hiking      | singing | collecting | baking  |
| Transport     | ship        | trike     | roller   | jet-ski  |

