 7. the nurse is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is chess##7
 8. the journalist is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
10. the doctor is the person who growsmarigold##1
