.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, sprite, water
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, grapes, onion, tomato
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, october, november, april
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, emerald, blue, chestnut
 1. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in march##7
 2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person drinking water##7
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
 4. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person who likes emerald##5
 5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person who likes chestnut##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 8. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person eating tomato##7
10. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
12. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person who's birthday is in november is not the person who likes emerald##6
14. the person who's birthday is in october is not the person eating onion##6
15. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the person who likes coral and the person eating grapes##7

.:: Answer ::.
