.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, amber, blue, lilac
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, mystery, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, french, malaysian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, alhambra, oliveros, baccarat
 1. the baccarat-smoker is the person who likes amber##1
 2. the brazilian is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 3. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
 4. the french is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 5. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the left of the french##5
 6. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 7. the person who likes amber is somewhere between the dunhill-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##7
 8. the person who likes lilac is not the dunhill-smoker##6
 9. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
10. the person watching action movies is on the left of the french##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person who likes amber is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Color         | turquise      | amber   | lilac   | blue       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action    | disaster | mystery       |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | colombian | french   | malaysian     |
| Cigar         | dunhill   | baccarat    | alhambra   | oliveros |

