.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, mirinda, tea
There 4 different types of food: apricot, artichoke, lemon, pear
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, dancer, designer, paramedic
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, december, may, april
 1. the paramedic is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person eating apricot##5
 3. the paramedic is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 4. the nurse is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is not the person who's birthday is in december##6
 6. the paramedic is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person eating pear##7
 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
10. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the paramedic##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating lemon##1
12. the person eating lemon is not the person who's birthday is in may##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk   | tea     | mirinda   | iced-tea |
| Food       | pear   | apricot | artichoke | lemon    |
| Job      | designer | paramedic | nurse   | dancer  |
| Birthday        | april | august     | may   | december |

