.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indian, malaysian, argentine
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, chess, filmmaking
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, designer, police-officer, writer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, july, june, april
 1. the indian is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's hobby is chess and the architect##2
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 4. the malaysian is on the far right##1
 5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is not the police-officer##6
 7. the police-officer is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
 9. the writer is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
10. the indian is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
11. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person who's hobby is chess is not the indian##6
13. the police-officer is on the left of the writer##1
14. the architect is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
15. the designer is on the left or right of the argentine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
