.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
House: palace, modern, cape-cod, cottage
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, fisherman, musician, videographer
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, snowmobile, car, motorbike
 1. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
 2. the musician is the cape-cod house##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is between the cottage house and the modern house##2
 5. the architect is somewhere to the right of the modern house##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the musician and the palace house##7
 7. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the person driving the airplane##1
 9. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
10. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the car is in an even position##4
12. the architect is somewhere to the right of the modern house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| House   | cottage      | cape-cod     | modern   | palace    |
| Job     | videographer | musician   | fisherman | architect |
| Pet     | snake        | rabbit     | goldfish  | pony      |
| Transport   | snowmobile       | motorbike | airplane   | car    |

 